org.perfidix.example.list

Class Array

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfidix.example.list.Array

  • public final class Array
extends Object
    This class provides convenience methods for handling arrays and serves as an extension to the Arrays class of Java.
    Author:
    BaseX Team 2005-11, BSD License, Christian Gruen
